ZH: 大伙儿一起来庆祝我的生日。
EN: Everyone come together to celebrate my birthday.

ZH: 我们大伙儿一起去看电影吧。
EN: Let's all go watch a movie together.

ZH: 大伙儿都加油，我们一定能成功的。
EN: Everyone, let's work hard, we will definitely succeed.

ZH: 今天大伙儿都穿红色衣服，庆祝中国的新年。
EN: Today, let's all wear red clothes to celebrate Chinese New Year.

ZH: 这个周末大伙儿一起去郊游，享受大自然。
EN: This weekend, let's all go on an outing together and enjoy nature.

ZH: 大伙儿又聚在一起，谈论着上大学的种种事情。
EN: Everyone gathered together again, discussing various matters about going to college.

ZH: 大伙儿都感到非常兴奋，因为明天是周末。
EN: Everyone is feeling very excited because tomorrow is the weekend.

ZH: 不要忘了提醒大伙儿明天要开会。
EN: Don't forget to remind everyone that we have a meeting tomorrow.

ZH: 大伙儿吃饭之前，先洗洗手。
EN: Before we eat, let's wash our hands first, everyone.

ZH: 请大伙儿各自写下自己的名字。
EN: Please everyone write down your names.

ZH: 大伙儿都安静下来，让我给你们介绍一下新同事。
EN: Everyone please quiet down, let me introduce the new colleague to you.

ZH: 大伙儿一起工作，我们比单独工作更高效。
EN: We work better together as a team than individually.

ZH: 今天的任务很艰巨，但只要大伙儿团结一心，就能完成。
EN: Today's task is challenging, but as long as we all work together, we can accomplish it.

ZH: 大伙儿都很有经验，我们可以相互学习。
EN: Everyone has a lot of experience, we can learn from each other.

ZH: 大伙儿早点起床，我们要赶火车。
EN: Let's all wake up early, we have to catch the train.

ZH: 大伙儿一起合作解决这个问题。
EN: Let's all work together to solve this problem.

ZH: 大伙儿的意见都很重要，我们要共同决定。
EN: Everyone's opinion is important, we need to decide together.

ZH: 大伙儿一定要记住今天的课程安排。
EN: Everyone must remember today's class schedule.

ZH: 大伙儿都非常高兴见到你！
EN: Everyone is very happy to see you!

ZH: 大伙儿一起举杯庆祝这个特殊的日子。
EN: Let's all raise our glasses together to celebrate this special day.
